: [[Elia Kazan]] – [[Endstation Sehnsucht (1951)|Endstation Sehnsucht]] ''(A Streetcar Named Desire)''
: [[Vincente Minnelli]] – [[Ein Amerikaner in Paris (Film)|Ein Amerikaner in Paris]] ''(An American in Paris)''
: [[William Wyler]] – [[Polizeirevier 21]] ''(Detective Story)''

